---
export const prerender = true;
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<style is:global>
.content-wrap { max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 48px 20px 80px; }
.content-section { margin-bottom: 48px; }
.content-section h2 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: clamp(20px,4vw,26px); font-weight: 700; color: var(--dark); margin-bottom: 16px; padding-bottom: 10px; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--pink-pale); }
.content-section h3 { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--dark); margin: 20px 0 8px; }
.content-section p { font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.75; color: var(--mid); margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: 300; }
.content-section p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
.content-section a { color: var(--pink); }
.content-section strong { color: var(--text); font-weight: 600; }
.shipping-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 16px 0; font-size: 14px; }
.shipping-table th { background: var(--pink-pale); color: var(--dark); font-weight: 600; padding: 10px 14px; text-align: left; border: 1px solid rgba(255,107,157,.15); }
.shipping-table td { padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgba(60,20,40,.07); color: var(--mid); }
.shipping-table tr:nth-child(even) td { background: rgba(255,248,240,.6); }
.info-box { background: var(--pink-pale); border-left: 4px solid var(--pink); border-radius: 0 var(--radius-sm) var(--radius-sm) 0; padding: 16px 18px; margin: 16px 0; font-size: 14px; color: var(--mid); line-height: 1.65; }
.info-box strong { color: var(--text); }
.steps-list { list-style: none; counter-reset: steps; margin: 12px 0; }
.steps-list li { counter-increment: steps; display: flex; gap: 14px; align-items: flex-start; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.65; color: var(--mid); }
.steps-list li::before { content: counter(steps); width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--grad-pink); color: white; font-weight: 700; font-size: 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; }
@media (min-width: 1024px) {
  .content-wrap { padding: 64px 40px 100px; }
  .content-section h2 { font-size: 28px; }
  .content-section p, .steps-list li, .info-box { font-size: 15px; }
}
</style>

<BaseLayout
  lang="en"
  title="Shipping and Returns | Creative Solace"
  description="Shipping rates, delivery times, and return policy for Creative Solace. Free shipping in the Netherlands. 14-day returns under EU consumer law. Damage reporting within 72 hours."
  canonical="https://creativesolace.com/shipping"
  ogTitle="Shipping and Returns | Creative Solace"
  ogDescription="Free NL shipping, 14-day EU returns, and damage policy for Creative Solace rhinestone kits."
  ogUrl="https://creativesolace.com/shipping"
  hreflangEn="https://creativesolace.com/shipping"
  hreflangNl="https://creativesolace.com/nl/shipping"
  heroLabel="Help"
  heroTitle="Shipping and"
  heroTitleEm="returns"
  heroSub="Everything you need to know about how your order gets to you, and what happens if something goes wrong."
  breadcrumb="Shipping and Returns"
>

  <div class="content-wrap">

    <div class="content-section">
      <h2>Shipping</h2>
      <h3>How fast do we ship?</h3>
      <p>We aim to pack and ship every order within <strong>1 to 3 business days</strong> of payment. You will receive a confirmation email with a track and trace link once your order is dispatched.</p>
      <h3>Shipping rates</h3>
      <table class="shipping-table">
        <thead>
          <tr><th>Destination</th><th>Cost</th><th>Estimated delivery</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>Netherlands</td><td><strong>Free</strong></td><td>1 to 3 business days</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Belgium and Germany</td><td>Calculated at checkout</td><td>2 to 5 business days</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Rest of Europe</td><td>Calculated at checkout</td><td>3 to 7 business days</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
      <p>Shipping costs are shown at checkout before you confirm payment.</p>
      <h3>Wrong shipping address</h3>
      <p>Please double-check your shipping address before placing your order. If you made a mistake, email <a href="mailto:hello@creativesolace.com">hello@creativesolace.com</a> within <strong>24 hours</strong> of purchase. After that we cannot guarantee we can make changes.</p>
      <h3>Delayed or lost packages</h3>
      <p>If your order has not arrived within 10 business days of your dispatch notification, please contact us and we will help you investigate with the courier.</p>
      <p>We are not responsible for delays caused by the courier, weather, or customs. For international orders, import duties are the responsibility of the buyer.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section">
      <h2>Returns</h2>
      <div class="info-box"><strong>Your right under EU law:</strong> under the Consumer Rights Directive, you have 14 days from the date of delivery to return your purchase without giving a reason.</div>
      <h3>How to return</h3>
      <ol class="steps-list">
        <li>Email <a href="mailto:hello@creativesolace.com">hello@creativesolace.com</a> with your order number and the reason for your return.</li>
        <li>We will confirm the return and provide the return address.</li>
        <li>Pack the item securely and send it back within 14 days of your return request.</li>
        <li>Once we receive and inspect the item, we will process your refund within 14 days.</li>
      </ol>
      <h3>Condition of returned items</h3>
      <p>To be eligible for a refund, the kit must be <strong>unused and in its original packaging</strong> with the B7000 adhesive seal intact. Kits that have been opened and used cannot be returned.</p>
      <h3>Return shipping costs</h3>
      <p>Return shipping costs are your responsibility, unless the item was delivered damaged, defective, or incorrectly. We recommend using a tracked service so the return is insured.</p>
      <h3>Refunds</h3>
      <p>Once your return has been received and approved, your refund will be processed to your original payment method within <strong>14 days</strong>. You will receive a confirmation email when the refund is issued.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section">
      <h2>Damaged or Defective Items</h2>
      <p>We take great care packing every order. If your item arrives damaged or defective:</p>
      <ol class="steps-list">
        <li>Take a photo of the damage.</li>
        <li>Email <a href="mailto:hello@creativesolace.com">hello@creativesolace.com</a> within <strong>72 hours</strong> of delivery.</li>
        <li>Include your order number and the photo.</li>
      </ol>
      <p>We will replace or refund the item at no extra cost to you. Minor dents to the outer box that do not affect the product inside do not qualify for replacement.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section">
      <h2>Workshop Tickets and Bookings</h2>
      <p>Workshop and event tickets are <strong>non-refundable</strong> once purchased, unless the event is cancelled by Creative Solace. If we cancel, you will receive a full refund within 14 days.</p>
      <p>If you booked via our quote form and can no longer attend, please let us know as soon as possible by emailing <a href="mailto:hello@creativesolace.com">hello@creativesolace.com</a>. We will do our best to find an alternative date for you.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section">
      <h2>Contact Us</h2>
      <p>For any questions about your order, a return, or a refund, contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@creativesolace.com">hello@creativesolace.com</a>. We respond within one business day.</p>
      <p>You can also visit our <a href="/faq">FAQ page</a> for quick answers to common questions.</p>
    </div>

  </div>

</BaseLayout>
